    sahu

    Personal R function library

    This is a work in progress. Just to try out added function who()

    Instructions to self:

    require(devtools)
devtools::install_github("sk-sahu/sahu")

    Fow now

    library(sahu)
sahu::who()

    More functionalities will be adding soon.

    Use functions via API: sk-sahu.ocpu.io/sahu
